    "description": "Full API collection for the SupportGenie Document Ingestion & Vector Embedding Pipeline.\n\nEndpoints:\n- Health Check\n- Upload PDF (multipart)\n- Add URL (JSON)\n- Add Text (JSON)\n- List Documents\n- Delete Document\n- Auth Failure scenarios\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:3000\nAuth: Bearer token in Authorization header",
